{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.720", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gr\u00fc\u00df Gott, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.840", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.200", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.440", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Verabredungen von Union und SPD zum Befristungsrecht gehen dahin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.240", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Befristungsrecht umfassend zu reformieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.680", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sorgen f\u00fcr mehr Rechtssicherheit f\u00fcr die Arbeitnehmerinnen und Arbeitnehmer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.360", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die befristet besch\u00e4ftigt sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.320", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem wir den Interessenausgleich zwischen dem Flexibilit\u00e4tsbed\u00fcrfnis der Arbeitgeber auf der einen Seite und dem Sicherheitsbed\u00fcrfnis der Arbeitnehmer auf der anderen Seite noch einmal deutlich zugunsten der Arbeitnehmer justieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.080", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist das zentrale Ergebnis unserer Verhandlungen in diesem Bereich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.120", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und ich finde das auch gut."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.240", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Mittelpunkt der Unionspolitik steht dabei nicht die sachgrundlose Befristung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.160", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Grunde haben wir hier durch die Regelungen in diesem Bereich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.080", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum Beispiel durch die H\u00f6chstfristen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.680", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein schon relativ stark reguliertes Instrument. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.920", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.560", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was uns bedr\u00e4ngt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.960", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist doch die Lage derjenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.960", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich von Befristung zu Befristung hangeln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.080", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo \u00fcber viele Jahre hinweg ein Sachgrund nach dem anderen aneinandergeh\u00e4ngt wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.240", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb haben die Betroffenen keine Planungssicherheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.960", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "keine verl\u00e4ssliche Perspektive f\u00fcr ihre Lebensplanung,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.360", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn es beispielsweise darum geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.120", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine Familie zu gr\u00fcnden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.760", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein Haus zu bauen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.640", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das f\u00fchrt zum Teil auch zu gesundheitlichen Einschr\u00e4nkungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.920", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau diese Lebensperspektive geben wir ein St\u00fcck weit zur\u00fcck, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.560", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem wir die Kettenbefristungen reformieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.400", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier gibt es bislang keine zeitlichen Begrenzungen durch den Gesetzgeber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.400", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das \u00e4ndern wir. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.200", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir \u00e4ndern dies, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.320", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil die Rechtsprechung des Bundesarbeitsgerichtes zwar feinziseliert ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.000", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber wenig mit Rechtssicherheit und Rechtsklarheit f\u00fcr den Rechtsanwender zu tun hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.320", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sagen ganz klar: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.560", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach f\u00fcnf Jahren Befristung ist Schluss."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.360", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann gibt es keine weitere Befristung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.840", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit sorgen wir f\u00fcr Rechtssicherheit und Rechtsklarheit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.080", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist das zentrale Anliegen der Unionspolitik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.280", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hier f\u00fcr mehr Rechtssicherheit f\u00fcr die Arbeitnehmerinnen und Arbeitnehmer zu sorgen und gerade ihr Sicherheitsbed\u00fcrfnis in diesem Bereich zu st\u00e4rken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.960", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.480", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gestatten Sie eine Zwischenfrage?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.400", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Selbstverst\u00e4ndlich gerne, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.440", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.400", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau M\u00fcller-Gemmeke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.200", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bitte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.720", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.000", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "selbstverst\u00e4ndlich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.560", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.960", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.840", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich habe vorhin geredet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.080", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber gerade deswegen habe ich jetzt noch eine Frage."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.520", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.800", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass bei den Kettenbefristungen etwas gemacht wird; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.320", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das unterst\u00fctzen wir. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.840", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das habe ich vorhin zwar nicht gesagt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.120", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber das sage ich jetzt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.400", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.520", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist doch gut. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.640", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr gut!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.360", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe vorhin ein Problem bei der sachgrundlosen Befristung geschildert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.600", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ja wohl uns\u00e4glich ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.800", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was wollen Sie gegen diese \u00fcblen Formen der sachgrundlosen Befristung machen?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.360", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schauen Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.240", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Frau Kollegin M\u00fcller-Gemmeke: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.440", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir erkennen das Flexibilit\u00e4tsbed\u00fcrfnis der Unternehmen im Hinblick auf die sachgrundlose Befristung an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.040", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie ist das einzige Instrument, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.680", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das in diesem Bereich relativ unb\u00fcrokratisch ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.520", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wir ver\u00e4ndern dieses Instrument auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.560", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem wir beispielsweise die H\u00f6chstfristen senken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.600", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir ver\u00e4ndern auch die Regelungen zu den Verl\u00e4ngerungsm\u00f6glichkeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.520", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bisher war eine dreimalige Verl\u00e4ngerung in maximal zwei Jahren m\u00f6glich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.120", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Zukunft wird nur noch eine einmalige Verl\u00e4ngerung m\u00f6glich sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.640", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gleichzeitig f\u00fchren wir bei der sachgrundlosen Befristung eine Quotierung innerhalb des jeweiligen Unternehmens ein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.000", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dies f\u00fchrt dazu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.600", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir einen massiven Eingriff in das Recht der sachgrundlosen Befristung vornehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.760", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch zugunsten der Arbeitnehmerinnen und Arbeitnehmer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.240", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.280", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist in Ordnung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.360", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir das tun. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.200", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wir d\u00fcrfen das Instrument der sachgrundlosen Befristung nicht einfach streichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.160", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil es eben auch das Bed\u00fcrfnis der Arbeitgeberseite nach Flexibilisierung gibt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.760", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn es um das Thema Missbrauch geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.560", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind wir uns einig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.400", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nat\u00fcrlich wollen auch wir keinen Missbrauch von befristeter Besch\u00e4ftigung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.840", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen werden wir gemeinsam \u00fcberlegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.160", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir das insgesamt gestalten k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.720", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.960", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Verabredungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.640", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Union und SPD im Rahmen der Koalitionsverhandlungen gemeinsam getroffen haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.520", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind gut und tragf\u00e4hig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.520", 
